&lt;p&gt;Please submit your resume and LinkedIn profile. Feel free to include a brief note introducing

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Role:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;We’re an AI Website Builder that allows businesses to create beautiful and functional websites. B12 is launching a new expert marketplace that connects top-tier web designers, freelancers, and agencies with B12 users who need help creating and refining their websites and digital marketing. If you love crafting and growing websites and are looking for an exciting new challenge, we’d love for you to apply!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As an expert in our partner ecosystem, you’ll have the opportunity to work directly with clients who use B12. You can expect to receive projects and referrals through our platform.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a freelancing opportunity ideal for those passionate about building custom websites and thriving in a creative, open environment. We’re selectively onboarding partners into the program and are excited to see the unique contributions you can bring.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Be Doing:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Working directly with B12 users/clients and applying your expertise in areas such as marketing, web design, or web development.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Becoming an active part of the B12 community, collaborating with other partners, and sharing feedback with the B12 team.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mastering B12’s product, particularly our AI-powered website editor, to help users quickly grow and build their websites.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;As a product expert, you’ll have the opportunity to become proficient with the B12 website editor and potentially gain early access to new opportunities within the B12 ecosystem.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We’re Looking for Someone Who:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Has Expertise:&lt;/strong&gt; 3-5 years of professional experience in your area of specialization (web design, marketing, web development).&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Is Comfortable Using the B12 Product:&lt;/strong&gt; You’re confident in leveraging B12’s tools to help our customers grow.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Communicates Well:&lt;/strong&gt; You have excellent written communication skills and enjoy collaborating with clients we send your way.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Is Flexible and Thrives in a Fast-Paced Environment:&lt;/strong&gt; You’re excited by the challenge of quickly delivering high-quality websites and seamlessly transitioning between projects.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Is Eager to Learn:&lt;/strong&gt; You’re open to mastering new tools, especially our Design Suite.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bonus Points If:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You’ve worked with small to medium-sized businesses before and understand their unique design needs.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have experience with UI/UX principles or other relevant design tools.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You’re comfortable navigating ambiguity and turning customer requests into well-structured designs.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
